{"tid":1196641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我已經支持咗香港10年所以今日理直氣壯上深圳玩","createTime":"2019-06-09T22:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T22:56:30.000Z","uid":160010,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a8c893df4dafec27dae2978593dd75c047be9df","tid":1196641,"uid":160010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:09:06.000Z","msg":"今日成班為咗打卡既傻尻上街 仲唔係我翻深圳玩既日子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zguHOeC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzguHOeC.png&h=6dce5a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地冇資格批評我嫁 我係我老母個閪到個陣已經反緊中共喇 我唔係香港人唔通你班打卡撚係啊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ca0oxGi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fca0oxGi.png&h=4c365127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都撐咗香港咁多年 抖一次係咪唔得啊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你玩你事 玩完仲要懶係野咁打段咁既野做乜？想表達啲乜？早人幾年玩社運係香港英雄？定係你今日唔行岀嚟好有理據？優越感從何而來？今日唔企岀嚟唔緊要 但做完港豬又要拎翻個牌坊咁 你仲嘔心過班為打卡而行岀嚟既人。"},{"pid":"175a54c04188e9e2d06ddd24477c8568c72b45c2","tid":1196641,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:52:11.000Z","msg":"北上做雞呀？"},{"pid":"58c694feca6288664e82ccccbc849089356e539b","tid":1196641,"uid":91192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:54:19.000Z","msg":"who.jpg"},{"pid":"35ebd95bd4c3cea1e6ee8c238a795d9ce3b5918d","tid":1196641,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"175a54c04188e9e2d06ddd24477c8568c72b45c2","tid":1196641,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:52:11.000Z","msg":"北上做雞呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:56:30.000Z","msg":"死臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔配做香港人"}]}